desc_short	-----								You are John T. Longy, a night-watchman at JUPITER, a secret base, set in an old, partially abandoned research facility in a remote countryside location. JUPITER is the main laboratory of the OLYMPUS GROUP.							
developer									Z4G0 and Ivan Venturi Productions								
